#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:26
msgid "Proxy Settings"
msgstr "Configuración de proxy"

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:27
msgid ""
"Every website has a limit to certain number of requests allowed for a certain period of time from an particular IP Address, exceeding the limit will block any incoming requests from that particular IP Address for a specific period of time.\n"
"          This results in unreliable recon results. Suppose if you were to run Nuclei on a particular target with all the templates, your IP is likely to get banned because of the number of requests made by Nuclei."
msgstr ""
"Todo sitio web tiene un límite en la cantidad de solicitudes permitidas durante cierto período de tiempo desde una dirección IP en particular; superar el límite bloqueará cualquier solicitud entrante desde esa dirección IP por un período específico de tiempo.\n"
"          Esto resulta en resultados de reconocimiento poco fiables. Supongamos que ejecuta Nuclei sobre un objetivo en particular con todas las plantillas: es probable que su IP sea baneada debido a la cantidad de solicitudes realizadas por Nuclei."

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:30
msgid "And this is especially true for dorking and other OSINT Suricatoos does. After certain dorking attempts Google is likely to ban your IP for certain period of time."
msgstr "Y esto es especialmente cierto para el dorking y otras actividades de OSINT que realiza Suricatoos. Tras ciertos intentos de dorking, es probable que Google banee su IP por un determinado período de tiempo."

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:33
msgid "Using proxies is recommended."
msgstr "Se recomienda el uso de proxies."

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:39
msgid "Use Proxy"
msgstr "Usar proxy"

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:41
msgid "Proxy List"
msgstr "Lista de proxies"

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:42
msgid "You can enter as many proxies as you want, Suricatoos will <span class=\"text-primary\">randomly</span> pick one among them during the scan."
msgstr "Puede ingresar tantos proxies como desee; Suricatoos elegirá <span class=\"text-primary\">aleatoriamente</span> uno de ellos durante el escaneo."

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:43
msgid "Separate the proxies by new line."
msgstr "Separe los proxies por nueva línea."

#: scanEngine/templates/scanEngine/settings/proxy.html:45
msgid "Save Proxies"
msgstr "Guardar proxies"

